snippet.title: Vikings: Valhalla | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Earn your place among the gods in this strategy game based on the hit series. Build your settlement and lead raids against rivals to become a legend.

Play Vikings: Valhalla on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81597685

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 238 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
